  "texts": [
    "These catalogues are marked with an asterisk (*) in the table header alongside the catalogue names.",
    "In addition, it is worth mentioning that the catalogues listed in Table 2 are not the same type of system.",
    "Indeed, some are ontology lookup services/repositories (e.g.",
    "AgroPortal and the EBI Ontology Lookup Service), while others are wider registries of standards/databases/policies (e.g., FAIRsharing) that include, but are not limited to, ontologies or other semantic artefacts.",
    "As such, their original intended scope and functionalities are inevitably different."
  ],
